      </p>
      <a
        class="inline-flex border-b-2 border-yellow-500 text-base font-medium text-black hover:bg-yellow-500 dark:text-gray-100 dark:hover:text-black"
        href="https://medium.com/singtel-digital-technology/modernising-an-enterprise-front-end-stack-fe0571f259a1"
        >Read more
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          class="h-6 w-6"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"
          />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </li>
  </ul>
</div>
